statement.markdown:
Create an accessible alert component that can be dismissed by the user. The alert should display the given message, have a close button, and be dismissible.
requirements
{"id":1,"text":"The alert should have a visually hidden heading with the text &#x27;Alert&#x27;."}
{"id":2,"text":"The alert should have a close button on the top right corner. The button should have an accessible name of &#x27;Dismiss&#x27;, and its text should be &#x27;Close&#x27;."}
{"id":3,"text":"The alert should be dismissible by clicking on the close button. When dismissed, the alert should be removed from the DOM."}
{"id":4,"text":"The alert should be focusable and have a focus trap for keyboard navigation."}

